   File: Components/Pages/Admin/StorageAdmin.razor

   PURPOSE: Admin-only page for monitoring backup status and
   manually triggering backup/restore operations.

   KEY CONCEPTS:
   • This page injects both SqliteBackupService (for status checks
     and direct restore) and BackupQueueService (for queued backups).
   • The "Backup Now" button uses BackupQueueService.RunBackupAndWaitAsync()
     so the spinner shows until the backup actually completes.
   • The "Restore" button uses SqliteBackupService.RestoreLatestAsync()
     directly because restore is a destructive operation that shouldn't
     be queued — the admin needs to see the result immediately.
   ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━ *@

